 Scotland, notably  Robert the Bruce  (  1274–1329 ), who freed Scotland from English domination. The altered short form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Robert Maitland was born in 1435, in Auckingill, Caithness, Scotland, United Kingdom as the son of John Maitland. He married Maria Scrymshire in 1455, in Auckingill, Caithness, Scotland, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"1435–":"1435–Surnud","1435–Male":"1435–Surnud","1440–Female":"1440–Surnud","1470–1550":"1470–1550","1385–Male":"1385–Surnud","1435":"1435","1455":"1455","1385":"1385","1550":"1550","1440":"1440","1470":"1470","Auchingill, , Caithness, Scotland":"Auckingill, Caithness, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Caithness, Scotland":"Caithness, Scotland"},"fi":{"1435–":"1435–Kuollut","1435–Male":"1435–Kuollut","1440–Female":"1440–Kuollut","1470–1550":"1470–1550","1385–Male":"1385–Kuollut","1435":"1435","1455":"1455","1385":"1385","1550":"1550","1440":"1440","1470":"1470","Auchingill, , Caithness, Scotland":"Auckingill, Caithness, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Caithness, Scotland":"Caithness, Scotland"},"fr":{"1435–":"1435–Décédé","1435–Male":"1435–Décédé","1440–Female":"1440–Décédée","1470–1550":"1470–1550","1385–Male":"1385–Décédé","1435":"1435","1455":"1455","1385":"1385","1550":"1550","1440":"1440","1470":"1470","Auchingill, , Caithness, Scotland":"Auckingill, Caithness, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","Caithness, Scotland":"Caithness, Écosse","lifeSummary":"Robert Maitland est né en 1435, à Auckingill, Caithness, Écosse, Royaume-Uni, fils de John Maitland. Il a épousé Maria Scrymshire en 1455, à Auckingill, Caithness, Écosse, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"1435–":"1435–Verstorben","1435–Male":"1435–Verstorben","1440–Female":"1440–Verstorben","1470–1550":"1470–1550","1385–Male":"1385–Verstorben","1435":"1435","1455